<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>VILLA YASUMIBA Okinawa Uruma | 東海岸には、あなたが知らない沖縄がある。</title>
  <meta name="description" content="沖縄県うるま市の一棟貸し、Independent House 沖縄VILLA YASUMIBA Okinawa Uruma。海中道路や離島へ向かう東海岸の滞在拠点。">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Old+Mincho:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400;1,600&amp;family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500&amp;family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@500&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --base: #F8F5F0;
      --ink: #1C1C1A;
      --accent: #C95F3A;
      --brown: #7A6652;
      --line: #E6DED4;
      --paper: #FFFDFC;
      --soft: rgba(230, 222, 212, 0.42);
      --serif: "Zen Old Mincho", serif;
      --sans: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      --en: "Cormorant Garamond", "Times New Roman", serif;
      --banner: "Plus Jakarta Sans", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; overflow-x: clip; }
    body { overflow-x: hidden; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-width: 320px;
      background: var(--base);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.95;
      word-break: keep-all;
      line-break: strict;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
    }

    img, iframe { display: block; width: 100%; }
    img { height: auto; object-fit: cover; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    h1, h2, h3, p, figure, blockquote { margin: 0; }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      overflow-wrap: normal;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.28;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    h3 {
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    button, .cta {
      min-height: 48px;
    }

    .lp-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      padding-top: 0;
      padding-bottom: 82px;
    }

    .section {
      position: relative;
      padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 116px) 24px;
    }

    .section-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(1120px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .kicker {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      line-height: 1.45;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 4.25rem);
    }

    .section-copy {
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--brown);
      line-height: 2.08;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 13px 22px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.35;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
    }

    .button:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .button.dark { background: var(--ink); color: var(--base); }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100svh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: clamp(116px, 13vw, 174px) 24px clamp(68px, 8vw, 104px);
      color: #fff;
      background:
        linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.76), rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.35)),
        url("photos/spots/kafu-banta-hero.jpg") center / cover no-repeat;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto 0 0;
      z-index: 0;
      height: 38%;
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.66), transparent);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(1040px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      max-width: 760px;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, min(5vw, 8.4vh), 4.35rem);
      text-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hero-lead {
      max-width: 610px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 2;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    .section-wave {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: -1px;
      z-index: 0;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      line-height: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .section-wave svg {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 60px;
    }

    .features {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--base);
    }

    .features-grid {
      width: min(1120px, 100%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }

    .feature-item {
      min-height: 96px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px 16px;
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(248, 245, 240, 0.16);
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .feature-item:last-child { border-right: 1px solid rgba(248, 245, 240, 0.16); }

    .two-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 0.88fr);
      gap: clamp(34px, 6vw, 72px);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .two-col.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .two-col.reverse .text-col { order: 2; }
    .two-col.reverse .media-col { order: 1; }

    .area {
      background: var(--base);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .area::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -120px;
      right: -180px;
      z-index: 0;
      width: 520px;
      height: 520px;
      border-radius: 58% 42% 34% 66% / 50% 58% 42% 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 48% 48%, rgba(201, 95, 58, 0.12), transparent 70%);
      filter: blur(44px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .area .section-title,
    .care .section-title,
    .access .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.55vw, 3.35rem);
    }

    .area-copy {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      color: var(--brown);
      line-height: 2.08;
    }

    .photo-frame {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 520px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--paper);
    }

    .photo-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      min-height: inherit;
    }

    .photo-frame::after {
      content: attr(data-label);
      position: absolute;
      left: 18px;
      bottom: 18px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      background: rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.68);
      color: var(--base);
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .spot-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0;
      margin: 34px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .spot-list li {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 17px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .spot-list strong {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .care {
      background: var(--paper);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .care::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -70px;
      left: -120px;
      z-index: 0;
      width: 460px;
      height: 460px;
      border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 50% 60% 40% 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 52% 48%, rgba(230, 222, 212, 0.72), transparent 68%);
      filter: blur(34px);
      opacity: 0.3;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .care-quote {
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding-left: 18px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.1vw, 1.7rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .reviews {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--base);
    }

    .reviews-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .slider-track {
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .slider {
      display: flex;
      transition: transform 0.36s ease;
    }

    .slide {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .slider-nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .slider-dots {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .slider-arrow {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      min-height: 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--ink);
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1;
      padding: 0;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .slider-arrow:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .slider-arrow:disabled {
      opacity: 0.25;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .slider-dot {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      min-height: 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--line);
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .slider-dot.active {
      background: var(--accent);
      transform: none;
    }

    .slide {
      min-height: 280px;
      display: grid;
      align-content: center;
      gap: 22px;
      padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--paper);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .review-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .stars {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }

    .slide blockquote {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(1.18rem, 2.1vw, 1.8rem);
      line-height: 1.78;
    }

    .space {
      background: var(--paper);
    }

    .space-head {
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .card-grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .space-card {
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--base);
    }

    .space-card img {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .space-card h3 {
      min-height: 58px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      color: var(--brown);
      font-family: var(--en);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .access {
      background: #EFE9E0;
    }

    .access-card {
      display: grid;
      align-content: center;
      gap: 22px;
      min-height: 460px;
      padding: clamp(28px, 5vw, 52px);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--paper);
    }

    .access-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .access-list li {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .access-list strong {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .access-list a {
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .map-wrap {
      min-height: 460px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--base);
    }

    .map-wrap iframe {
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 460px;
      border: 0;
      filter: saturate(0.9) contrast(0.98);
    }

    .final-cta {
      padding: clamp(76px, 10vw, 120px) 24px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .final-cta .section-inner {
      display: grid;
      justify-items: center;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .final-cta h2 {
      max-width: 820px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 4.2rem);
    }

    .final-cta p {
      max-width: 640px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);
    }

    .fixed-cta {
      position: fixed;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      z-index: 900;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 12px 16px calc(12px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.1);
      background: rgba(248, 245, 240, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .fixed-cta .button {
      width: min(430px, 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(28, 28, 26, 0.16);
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .features-grid,
      .card-grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .two-col,
      .two-col.reverse {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .two-col.reverse .text-col,
      .two-col.reverse .media-col {
        order: initial;
      }

      .photo-frame,
      .access-card,
      .map-wrap,
      .map-wrap iframe {
        min-height: 380px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      body { font-size: 14px; }

      .section {
        padding: 62px 20px;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 100svh;
        padding: 98px 20px 54px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: clamp(1.84rem, 7.1vw, 2.12rem);
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      }

      .hero h1 br { display: none; }

      .hero-tagline {
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .hero-lead {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.95;
      }

      .hero-actions,
      .hero-actions .button {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .section-title,
      .area .section-title,
      .care .section-title,
      .access .section-title,
      .final-cta h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 8.4vw, 2.55rem);
      }

      .features-grid,
      .card-grid-3 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .feature-item {
        min-height: 72px;
        border-left: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(248, 245, 240, 0.16);
      }

      .feature-item:last-child { border-right: 0; }

      .photo-frame {
        min-height: 320px;
      }

      .spot-list li {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .reviews-head {
        display: block;
      }

      .slide blockquote {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .space-card img {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 11;
      }

      .map-wrap,
      .map-wrap iframe {
        min-height: 350px;
      }

      .fixed-cta {
        padding-left: 12px;
        padding-right: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="lp-wrapper">
    <header class="section hero">
      <!-- 写真差し込み: ヒーロー背景 — 建物外観または室内全景（広角・温かみのある光） -->
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="kicker">VILLA YASUMIBA OKINAWA URUMA</p>
        <h1>東海岸には、<wbr>あなたが知らない<wbr>沖縄がある。</h1>
        <p class="hero-tagline">YASUMIBAは東海岸を遊び尽くすのに最適な拠点。</p>
        <p class="hero-lead">
          地元の朝市。<br>
          誰もいないビーチ。<br>
          果報バンタ。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button cta" href="https://www.booking.com/hotel/jp/yasumiba.ja.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">空き日程を確認する</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-wave" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M0,30 C360,60 1080,0 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#F8F5F0" opacity="0.92"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="features" aria-label="宿の特徴">
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">1棟貸切</div>
        <div class="feature-item">最大10名</div>
        <div class="feature-item">Booking.com ★9.5</div>
        <div class="feature-item">海中道路まで車20分</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section area">
      <div class="section-wave" aria-hidden="true" style="top:0; bottom:auto; transform:rotate(180deg); opacity:.4;">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
          <path d="M0,30 C360,60 1080,0 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#E6DED4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="section-inner two-col">
        <div class="text-col">
          <p class="kicker">East Coast Route</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">こんな沖縄が、<wbr>あったのか。</h2>
          <div class="area-copy">
            <p>海中道路。与勝半島から平安座島まで、海の上を4.7kmの道路がまっすぐ走る。窓を開けると、潮風がダイレクトに入ってくる。その先に宮城島、さらに伊計島。橋でつながる島が、つづく。</p>
            <p>宮城島の崖の上に、「果報バンタ」がある。沖縄の言葉で、幸せの崖。断崖絶壁から見下ろすエメラルドグリーンの海は、静かで、人がいない。</p>
            <p>浜比嘉島には、石垣と赤瓦の民家が今も残っている。ガイドブックには載っていない。地元の人が昔から、普通に来ていた島。</p>
            <p>東海岸のビーチには、なぜかほとんど人がいない。西海岸と同じ沖縄の海なのに。</p>
          </div>
          <ul class="spot-list">
            <li><strong>海中道路</strong><span>車20分</span></li>
            <li><strong>伊計島・宮城島・浜比嘉島</strong><span>車40分（橋でつながる離島群）</span></li>
            <li><strong>果報バンタ</strong><span>車45分・入場無料</span></li>
            <li><strong>うるマルシェ</strong><span>車5分</span></li>
            <li><strong>勝連城跡</strong><span>車10分（世界遺産）</span></li>
            <li><strong>うるまの闘牛</strong><span>車15分</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="media-col">
          <!-- 写真差し込み: 海中道路・離島・果報バンタからエメラルドグリーンの海 -->
          <figure class="photo-frame" data-label="Kaichu road / Uruma coast">
            <img src="photos/spots/kaichu-road-1.jpg" alt="うるま市の海中道路" loading="lazy">
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section care">
      <div class="section-inner two-col reverse">
        <div class="text-col">
          <p class="kicker">Owner Care</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">何も考えずに、<wbr>休めた。</h2>
          <div class="section-copy">
            <p>冷蔵庫に、ゴーヤとジュース。</p>
            <p>ミキサー、ボードゲーム、何種類も。</p>
            <p>「あったらいいな」が全部あった。</p>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="care-quote">
            「5つ星ホテル以上の気配りを感じた」<br>
            ——Googleマップ、家族旅行のゲストより
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="media-col">
          <!-- 写真差し込み: 宿の入口・外観またはリビング全景 -->
          <figure class="photo-frame" data-label="Living / entrance">
